==Description==

The '''TechDraw ExtensionThreadHoleBottom''' tool adds a cosmetic thread to the top or bottom view of holes.

[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionThreadHoleBottomExample.png|200px]]
{{Caption|On the right a hole with a cosmetic thread}}

==Usage==

# Optionally specify the line attributes with the [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionSelectLineAttributes.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionSelectLineAttributes|TechDraw ExtensionSelectLineAttributes]] tool.
# Select one or more circles.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionThreadHoleBottom.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionThreadHoleBottom|Add Cosmetic Thread Hole Bottom View]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|TechDraw → Extensions: Centerlines/Threading → [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionThreadHoleBottom.svg|16px]] Add Cosmetic Thread Hole Bottom View}} option from the menu.
# Cosmetic threads are added.


